<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> fürgelegt
                                <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Hall<ex>er</ex></expan>, Karl Holczschüher, Hans Tücher und etliche
                                <expan>ande<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>e</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>
<add>von</add>
<expan>ir</expan> armen lewte <add><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan></add> czü
                        Hawsen bey Vorcheim gelegen, die in die pfarre gen Vorcheim hinein mit
                                <expan>pferrlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gehören, wie in
                            <expan>diselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ir <expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan> lewte
                        gesagt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz man sie von
                                <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> pfarre cze nemen und mit
                                <expan>pferrlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> anderswo hin cze weisen maine, <add>das in
                            gar swer sey, wan</add> sie <expan>besorge<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz sie
                        nicht als wol <expan>fürseh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein noch als wol awsgericht
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, als in <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> pfarre czü Vorcheim.
                            <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir ewr gnade darczü wenden und das
                                <expan>gnediklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürkume<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet, also daz
                            <expan>diselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> armen lewte bey
                            <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> pfarre czü Vorcheim, dahin sie
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> gehören,
                            <expan>beleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und davon nicht
                                <expan>geczoge<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, als etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> v in <expan>ebdom<ex>ine</ex></expan>
<expan>penthecost<ex>en</ex></expan>. </ab>
